<p><strong>Problem 1: Constant Messaging</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>"What's the WiFi password?"</li>
<li>"How does the AC work?"</li>
<li>"Where's the nearest 7-Eleven?"</li>
</ul>

<p><strong>Solution:</strong> Guest book answers all these questions instantly.</p>

<h2>Essential Guest Book Sections</h2>

<h3>Section 1: Welcome Message</h3>

<p>Keep it warm but professional.</p>

<pre><code>Welcome to [Property Name]!

