<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>Item</th>
<th>Details</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td><strong>WiFi</strong></td>
<td>Network: [Name] / Password: [Password]</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>Check-Out</strong></td>
<td>11:00 AM</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>Emergency</strong></td>
<td>+60 19-699 6688</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>Parking</strong></td>
<td>[Number] lots, [location]</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>

<h3>Section 3: House Rules</h3>

<p>Be clear, firm but polite.</p>

<ul>
<li><strong>Quiet Hours:</strong> 10:00 PM - 7:00 AM</li>
<li><strong>Smoking:</strong> NO smoking inside. RM 500 penalty</li>
<li><strong>Guests:</strong> Maximum [X] guests only</li>
</ul>

<h3>Section 4: Local Recommendations</h3>

<p>Guests LOVE local insider tips.</p>

<p><strong>Must-Visit Heritage Sites (Walking Distance):</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Jonker Street:</strong> 5 min walk - Night market on Fridays/Saturdays</li>
<li><strong>A Famosa Fortress:</strong> 3 min walk - Historical landmark</li>
<li><strong>Melaka River Cruise:</strong> 5 min walk - Scenic river tour</li>
</ul>

<p><strong>Best Local Food (Within 1km):</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Nancy's Kitchen:</strong> Jonker Street - Nyonya cuisine</li>
<li><strong>Baba Charlie:</strong> Traditional kuih</li>
<li><strong>Capital Satay:</strong> Satay celup</li>
</ul>

