<li>WiFi details</li>
<li>Appliance instructions</li>
<li>Check-out process</li>
<li>Local recommendations</li>
<li>Emergency contacts</li>
</ul>

<div class="my-8">
  <a href="https://wa.me/60196996688?text=Hi%20iHousing,%20I%20need%20a%20professional%20guest%20book%20for%20my%20Airbnb%20property." target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-block bg-green-600 text-white font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-green-700 transition">
    WhatsApp Us: +60 19-699 6688
  </a>
